description:
Create a middleware service that, given a Salesforce object, returns the list of Object Views that include that object. For example, if the Account object belongs to three saved views, the service returns those three views with their names and IDs.

This service supports a planned UX enhancement: a tab or selector on the object detail page that shows which views the current object belongs to, allowing users to quickly switch to a relevant view.

Implementation uses the existing Eloquent relationship between Scorecard (object) and ErdViews models:
```php
$objectID = 14;
$scorecard = Scorecard::find($objectID);
$views = $scorecard->erdViews;
```
